# Files excluded from the OTA runtimeVersion fingerprint.
#
# These hold ONLY the expo-updates runtime config (URL, check policy, and the
# runtimeVersion value itself). They must be excluded or writing the computed
# runtimeVersion back into them would change the fingerprint on every run
# (a feedback loop). Nothing in these files affects native compatibility, so
# ignoring them is safe — real native changes still live in the rest of
# ios/ and android/ and still bump the fingerprint.
ios/AnkaaDesign/Supporting/Expo.plist
android/app/src/main/res/values/expo_runtime.xml
